ng\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555644154a.png&h=f4be440c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555493098a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555493098a.jpg&h=667fcd14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555493061a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555493061a.jpg&h=3bd720c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555493180a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555493180a.jpg&h=f3ebdbf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555493228a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555493228a.jpg&h=c6f38f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.新手重點活動 每天登入<br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555319311a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555319311a.png&h=e88dc468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555673433a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555673433a.png&h=25c47081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.統合整備計劃<br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555483402a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555483402a.png&h=1f96ce59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/event/20190424/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fevent%2F20190424%2F&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=af3480fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/event/20190424/</a><br />\n<br />\n4.1日1回100BC <br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555570639a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555570639a.png&h=e379b4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555570684a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555570684a.png&h=ead6a855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.大規模戦比賽活動<br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1555492950a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1555492950a.jpg&h=2773fd68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.強化機率上昇5%<br />\n<img src=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/upload/201904/1554806170a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fupload%2F201904%2F1554806170a.jpg&h=8ed8b742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n24/4/2019 更新詳情連結<br />\n<a href=\"http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/member/information/article.php?no=2410&amp;utm_source=bno&amp;utm_medium=launcher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmsgo.bandainamco-ol.jp%2Fmember%2Finformation%2Farticle.php%3Fno%3D2410%26utm_source%3Dbno%26utm_medium%3Dlauncher&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=43204180\" target=\"_blank\">http://msgo.bandainamco-ol.jp/member/information/article.php?no=2410&amp;utm_source=bno&amp;utm_medium=launcher</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A <br />\n1.課金先有得玩? <br />\n答:唔係 無所謂既體力計限制 玩家可透過活動得到課金道具 <br />\n<br />\n2.使用VPN會很LAG? <br />\n答:不會 即使用不同的VPN都很順暢 <br />\n<br />\n3.有港服嗎? <br />\n答: <span style=\"color: red;\">曾經有(已執了)</span><br />\n<br />\n連登部隊 我們在SER1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一個SER就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地球連邦軍<br />\n部隊名  戦場の掃除屋 <br />\n隊長ID 白い狼<br />\n副隊長 KiRiTO<br />\n召募狀態: 召募中 <br />\n召募條件:<span style=\"color: red;\">不能使用中文角色名稱 請寫信比 副隊長／隊長</span> 申請入隊<br />\n<br />\n自護軍殘黨 <br />\n部隊名 月華刃 <br />\n隊長ID Siubak <br />\n召募狀態: 召募中 <br />\n召募條件: <span style=\"color: red;\">不能使用中文角色名稱 請寫信比隊長</span> 申請入隊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">搜尋隊長/副隊長ID請註明大細階! 否則會搜尋不能</span><br />\n<br />\n如何加入日服<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eF-fZZLYhp8&amp;t=3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeF-fZZLYhp8%26t%3D3s&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=ebd959f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eF-fZZLYhp8&amp;t=3s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/gfOYsI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FgfOYsI.gif&h=bcc81f7d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隻GAME唔撚識裝呀!屌你!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今期囡囡精選#19  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> zoeso0930<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTGHpx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTGHpx3.jpg&h=39aa0053&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79789e2d4d9bdda3df76555c285db053f08dab7b","tid":1121930,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T16:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d6ac90c740c10ed59aa03a1de668d5a20f1070","tid":1121930,"uid":160284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"有冇咩月費VPN 推薦下<br />\n而家用免費個啲成日打到一半就斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7294d9039345e70